{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> <strong>&quot;Shh, quiet. There's a monster outside.&quot;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765090/extras/1.gif?t=1732150027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the year 20XX after high school class is just finishing up... with a sudden earthquake and a quick flood of monsters sweeping in, this peaceful life is turned to chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The surviving protagonist and his friends try to escape the school they find themselves in, but then they realized they've been transported to this strange, far-off world...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>[ Game intro ]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On this maze-like path, their fates are all intertwined, so they must fight against the enemies that stand in their way in this dungeon crawling RPG, High School Crisis!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>[ Gameplay ]</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25b6\ufe0f [Upgrade] your stats and [Set] your skills to battle!\u25c0\ufe0f</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A new dynamic system that adds to the classic Dungeon RPG feel!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight off the never-ending waves of enemies as you look to escape this world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Combine a variety of skills to create a character just for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765090/extras/2.gif?t=1732150027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Don't let your guard down, even on the move! Every movement needs a strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765090/extras/3.gif?t=1732150027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Consider enemy attack patterns and attributes to turn the fight in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765090/extras/4.gif?t=1732150027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>\u25b6\ufe0fUtilize the unique personalities of your party members to raise your chances of success in battle!\u25c0\ufe0f</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each classmate has unique characteristics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765090/extras/5.gif?t=1732150027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Assign party members classes, such as weapon-based, magic-based, and assist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adjust behavior, order, or work to chain attacks with your partners!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765090/extras/6.gif?t=1732150027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>\u25b6\ufe0fWhat strange phenomenon brought you all here?\u25c0\ufe0f</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This story spells adventure as the boys and girls try to escape the vast world they've found themselves in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765090/extras/7.gif?t=1732150027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765090/extras/8.gif?t=1732150027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Within this demon realm, various characters, new enemies, and hidden secrets work to block the protagonist's way forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the end, what fate will they meet?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u203b Regarding gameplay upload and streaming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Any individual or company may stream or upload videos of this game as long as the copyright information and store URLs are included within the video description or the video itself. We would appreciate creators leaving out spoilers of the ending whenever possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a92024 PISOFT Co., Ltd. All Rights Reserved. Published by CFK.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Defeated Orthus","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2765090/5c65d079ae104a85f49f049abc2f835d0747601f.jpg"},{"name":"Girl in Danger 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2765090/f5a9d88988f6773ac4e839639b6e1fcebf40634e.jpg"},{"name":"MMC Obtained","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2765090/8e3092131a783e944beefce7751af9e2388e8f8d.jpg"},{"name":"To the City of Pleasure","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2765090/bb80e15c6580f747f0ea37c31a0dc43491fd6f88.jpg"},{"name":"Girl in Danger 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2765090/abc3805a232c6ca3247999f1b38aea359e65ada3.jpg"},{"name":"Defeated Naberius","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2765090/feab9aadd0f76072197edf4719d1a1b5ace00fa7.jpg"},{"name":"To the Tower of Enchantment","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2765